Subject:    Question about authoritive answers
From:       <a href="?a=95837816800042&r=1&w=2">zaphod.mps.ohio-state.edu!unix.cis.pitt.edu!dsinc!dsinc.DSI.COM!syd () tut ! cis ! ohio</a>
